Is `_layout.css` from the boilerplate designed to be used anywhere a 12-col grid is needed, or is designed to be specifically used with only the drag-and-drop HubL code?

The breakpoints seem to be a bit funny:
```@media (max-width: 767px) {}

@media (min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1139px) {}

@media (min-width: 1280px) {}```
It looks like the area between 1140px - 1179px is missing?
